A Kind Note on Commercial Use

EntraPass is published under the MIT License above, which is intentionally
permissive and allows broad use, modification, and distribution. We believe
strongly in open source and want this tool to be as useful as possible to
the community.

That said, if you are considering using EntraPass — or a derivative of it —
as part of a commercial product, paid service, or consulting engagement, we
kindly ask that you reach out to us before doing so. Commercial use is warmly
welcomed; we simply ask for a brief conversation first to ensure we can
support you properly and acknowledge the work appropriately.

Please get in touch at:
  Website: https://aboutcloud.io
  GitHub:  https://github.com/arusso-aboutcloud

Thank you for respecting the spirit of this project, and for helping make
phishing-resistant authentication more accessible to everyone.
